<div type="history" n="record">
<head>History of Recording</head>

<p>Complete text copied by Sherard in 1716 (10101, 128). A large fragment copied by Reichel (R I, 8);a smaller fragment, from the left side of ll.5-9, was recorded by Gaudin (38a). That fragment has not been found again, but the larger fragment found by Reichel and another small fragment were found by the NYU expedition in 1975.</p>
</div>
